;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;新数据显示，&lt;/strong&gt;战争和关税引发的美国通胀达到三年来的最高水平。波斯湾发生新的交火。人们对美联储今年不会降息的预期越来越强烈。所有这些都可以说会引起投资者的谨慎。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/bLUt1_WQvVRGlIwaib40DcscBQGlZC9eD0yU2C8wS8korKaA3ozjEUm6PCDJuEfJDJ4zWXR_EsQqc4nmp3veYKWCGPQ4ODf7HHLmibCkBI0iehFtFMuv0MQTy3W7YWZARiAXSOaxBwLWPLzTmyolefX-98S9iAYFeSCDQSHBN-BO4Y4B7Kz8GpiAgRF1dhBhzzwzJibg2xxnGB1tsc2aQTbQMPZyUkM350Hb3vHhTecsE6wfW-StgcagwPC_FtscnXj7rOLdIG84cWv3GS1NQgT5wXx4zVePtEc8G7zNb6QxFX82mEmfz2eoCINZMKXcGb6z3GNRRs9oObIvNRq1Cpxx3sIMO2XIkw__u041v2bkzSbjqp4SNtR_BwPhVImKJsV2pMreQAKDoIn_G9gxvWHpze6iXJhkrw9gXg_xXNpCDXeVHKmz0pndQzGzizZuXGouykKKPbMo1KXp4tBcwkzTop-7HvM-0ZF_8hdTS8ik6pCIAUt6AaXQGP1uU4G4rDX0MpNyiD_u560tjbFuj7GPbhY/Xx1eYkM2W7pm5dwsdKD66w_jILdPA3sJ/21" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iakYfwwhFJaw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iakYfwwhFJaw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;可以说。本周股市延续了自 2023 年以来最长的单周上涨&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/7_eDng5E0Kav0W5P78rK0ZaCu4jF4aevfOZFTOzdoX6Lb7qNzR19IHYDEtCXz5rgP3Q3txZmbJgR1C6X-6-0WOVCMMGMvnAs-uvQ4wX7XD65YGSSkXzDRU6WdSdUQM4qKWf4MuQgSIRa-a0e5qXvzfC77yMELE2a-OPslbmPbMZIDzkAbboY0-PsSX-8KwLHXDQQvMUhQYfo4SQ6zerZe0TgZYlz55okDAgI2oYJ-gs9UM0aKx97xQSzGtPrGTPyzcQtkqMwYLB0c8-Ut